title: Measuring Taste - Literature
description:
Now we turn to books—your taste, knowledge, and instincts.

You'll see novels, authors, and works from across eras and genres. Some questions are simple, others harder. There are no wrong answers—just what you enjoy, recall, or value.

Ready to explore your literary self?
